Text: get out in front of it

Author: ftphx
Text: Aw well he is probably very worried and concerned. Alot of people don't know how to approach the situation or are unsure even if all the signs of disordered eating are clear. Have you ever considered being the one to bring it up? He may be able to support you, if you two are close. Try not to stress over whether or not he saw the tabs, honestly theres a good chance he didnt. Guys can be incredibly oblivious to things right in front of them.... it's a thing. Here for you
